  ---

  Why AGPL v3 for Nuthatch:

  - Protects the project from being taken closed-source by a larger
    player (e.g. a cloud provider hosting a modified fork as a service
    without sharing their changes).
  - Encourages contributions back to the community.
  - Compatible with Wallos, Plausible, Grafana, Mattermost, Nextcloud,
    and other self-hosted tools in adjacent categories.
  - Allows us to offer a separate commercial license for organizations
    that can't comply with AGPL (see README for commercial license info).
